- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses algorithms for model checking. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is another possible category as the paper mentions applications to automata theory and parsing. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper mentions potential applications to games.
